<body>
    <section class="main">
        <div class="background-img"></div>
        <div class="main-content">
            <div id="company">Carr<span style="color: rgb(238, 84, 84);">Pedia</span></div>
            <div id="scroll">Scroll for contents.</div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <hr style="width: 65%; background-color: rgb(223, 223, 86); position: absolute; left: 18%; border-top: 3px solid rgb(228, 211, 64);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="intro">
            <h2 style="letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: center; padding: 40px 0; padding-bottom: 100px;">Welcome to CarrPedia. Love cars? Well then you landed in the just right website!</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="assets/bmw.png" alt="bmw logo_png">
                    <h3>Know about you favourite car brands, and the cars which they manufacture. Perfect for car fanactics!</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img src="assets/suzuki.png" alt="suzuki logo_png">
                    <h3>Also, get to know a brief history about your favourite car brands, about how they became a 'brand'.</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img style="width: 250px; height: 150px;" src="assets/fiat.png" alt="fiat logo_png">
                    <h3>Browse through a vast collection of photo gallery for every specific cars. Good for some quality wallpapers!</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <img style="width: 160px; height: 150px;" src="assets/ferrari.png" alt="ferrari logo_png">
                    <h3>Once registered, you can upload your own photos into the gallery, and contribute to the CarPedia gallery.</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div id="galleryjumbo" class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center;" class="row">
                <div class="col-md-9">
                    <div style="margin-top: 0;" class="page-header">
                        <h2>CarrGallery.</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p>CarrGallery is an awesome place for you to access loads of full HD pictures of your favourite cars. You can view or save them, and once registered, you can also post your own pictures and contribute to our gallery as well!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3">
                    <a href="/gallery" id="galleryexplore" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg ">Explore now</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="jumbotron">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div style="margin-top: 0;" class="page-header">
                        <h2><small>Introducing </small>CarrSuggest.</h2>
                    </div>
                    <p style="text-align: left;">CarrSuggest is simply a suggestion box, where users can contribute and help us grow by giving their suggestions and reviews
                        on the content of the website. You can suggest us what can else be done to improve CarrPedia, and we will do our best to implement
                        your suggestion. 
                     </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;" class="container">
                        <h2>CarrSuggest</h2>
                        <div  class="scrollable">
                            <table class="table">
                                <thead>
                                   <h4>Add you suggestions here.</h4> 
                                </thead>
                                <tbody class="suggestbody">
                                    
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <section class="form">
                            <input id="writeop" style="margin: 5px;" class="form-control text-center" type="text" placeholder="write your suggestions">
                            <button id="addop" style="margin: 5px;" class="btn btn-danger">Submit</button>
                        </section>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
